# ğŸ“Š E-Commerce Data Engineering Pipeline

## ğŸš€ Overview
This project implements an end-to-end batch ETL pipeline for processing e-commerce sales data and generating business analytics dashboards.

The pipeline extracts raw CSV sales data, performs data cleaning and business-level transformations, loads the processed data into MySQL, and visualizes KPIs using Streamlit.

